## Step 5 â€” Apply the Theme

### Option A â€” Apply globally (all dashboards for you)
1. Click your profile icon (bottom left corner)
2. Scroll down to **Theme**
3. Select **Aquarium** from the dropdown
4. Refresh the page

### Option B â€” Apply to one dashboard only
1. Open the dashboard you want to theme
2. Click â‹® (top right) â†’ **Edit Dashboard**
3. Click â‹® again â†’ **Raw Configuration Editor**
4. At the very top, add:
   ```yaml
   theme: aquarium
   title: ğŸŸ Freshwater Tank
   ```
5. Save

### Option C â€” Apply backend-selected theme
1. Settings â†’ System â†’ General
2. Set **Default theme** to **Aquarium**
3. All users will now see the aquarium theme by default

